snippet.title: Best VGM 1346 - Sonic CD - Quartz Quadrant ~ Present (JP / EU)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2161 - https://youtu.be/RpQlfTGfEsw

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Sega CD
Sonic the Hedgehog CD (1993)
Quartz Quadrant ~ Present (JP / EU)
Naofumi Hataya
